                            <comment id="12799681" author="fmeschbe" created="Wed, 13 Jan 2010 10:14:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rev. 898696: Redo sending the 401/UNAUTHORIZED status to just use setStatus and then flush the response. Don&apos;t use sendError to prevent any error handlers to kick in &amp;#8211; we really want the 401 status to be sent to the client.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
